name: self-service
description:
"self-service" by byng

I forget what time this photo was taken, I chose a pretty big aperture here at f.11 with a 30 seconds of shutter speed. The location I took this photo was in Depok, a small city in Indonesia, if u are wondering about.

the gear I use;
* Camera : Fujica MPF 105XN (35mm camera)
* Lens : EBC X-Fujinon f=1.6 50mm DM
* Film : Fujifilm Superia X-Tra 400

overexposure +1 with normal develop on local lab
